data.description: "Cute ranch style home, located in Flint Township on a private well, featuring an inviting living room with a large window to brighten this space. Lovely kitchen with all appliances included and a cozy eating area and doorwall leading out to the backyard with an above ground pool. Three spacious bedrooms with plenty of closet space, and a full bathroom with tile floor and a conveniently located half bath right off the garage. Full basement ready for someone's finishing touches. Nice oversized fenced in backyard for your enjoyment."
